---
// How It Works Section V1
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 bg-background">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-12">
      <!-- Título -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-4 animate-fade-in">
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary">Como Funciona</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
          Alcance a Aprovação em <span class="text-accent">3 Passos Simples</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Steps Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
        <!-- Connecting Line -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-24 h-0.5 bg-gradient-hero -z-10" style="width: 66%; left: 16.6%;"></div>
        
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="relative p-8 space-y-6 hover:shadow-elegant transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 bg-card rounded-lg border border-border">
          <div class="absolute -top-6 left-8 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-hero rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-foreground font-bold text-lg shadow-glow">
            01
          </div>
          
          <div class="pt-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-card rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Construa Seu Perfil de Herói</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Cadastre seus concursos-alvo, organize seus materiais de todos os cursinhos e defina suas metas. Simples e rápido.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="relative p-8 space-y-6 hover:shadow-elegant transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 bg-card rounded-lg border border-border">
          <div class="absolute -top-6 left-8 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-hero rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-foreground font-bold text-lg shadow-glow">
            02
          </div>
          
          <div class="pt-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-card rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ative Sua Super Inteligência AC</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Nossa IA analisa seu perfil, identifica lacunas de conhecimento e cria um plano de estudos personalizado e otimizado.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="relative p-8 space-y-6 hover:shadow-elegant transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 bg-card rounded-lg border border-border">
          <div class="absolute -top-6 left-8 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-hero rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary-foreground font-bold text-lg shadow-glow">
            03
          </div>
          
          <div class="pt-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-card rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Execute a Missão e Monitore o Progresso</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Siga seu ciclo de estudos, use flashcards dinâmicos, resumos inteligentes e acompanhe sua evolução em tempo real.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
